This pass works for :
1) only inner most loops .i.e when there is loop nest of depth>=2
2) inner most loop body does'nt has any conditional branches
3) can handle almost any "complex topology" of loop nest (see - test4_*.c in test folder) 

This pass currently can split innermost loops as many times needed, but will not change loop bounds.

Refrences:
https://llvm.org/docs/ProgrammersManual.html
https://llvm.org/docs/LangRef.html

LLVM DOXYGEN for going thrugh all teh API provided by different classes.

 
	     		
